{"tid":48457,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"奸商回收病毒針筒 再造餐具","createTime":"2016-12-21T05:44:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-02T08:24:40.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4aa45e68047f378930f3a92520a159feaf4a3646","tid":48457,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T05:44:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1575000/1576020/c03fd53e860e19c3353516_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1575000%2F1576020%2Fc03fd53e860e19c3353516_600.jpg&h=5b160694&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n蘇南京市公安局日前偵破醫療廢物污染環境案件，發現約3000多噸醫療廢棄物被轉賣到市場，部份被製成餐具、玩具等。 <br />\n<br />\n南京棲霞公安分局歷時3個多月，偵破這起案件，共3名嫌犯，其中1人被逮捕，2人被取保候審；現場查獲醫療廢棄物13.5噸，嫌犯收購、倒賣醫療廢物3000多噸，涉案價值4000多萬元（人民幣，下同）。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1575000/1576020/c03fd53e860e19c3353519_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1575000%2F1576020%2Fc03fd53e860e19c3353519_600.jpg&h=298299e5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n醫療廢棄物含有大量的致病細菌有害物質，不僅會造成環境污染，而且可能傳播疾病，因此一般要經特別處理，不可直接回收再造。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1575000/1576020/c03fd53e860e19c335351c_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1575000%2F1576020%2Fc03fd53e860e19c335351c_600.jpg&h=ffce2b88&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n部份亦用作材料 製造玩具 <br />\n<br />\n根據內地媒體報道說，8月29日，南京棲霞公安分局在對燕子磯顧家村一帶清查整治時，發現顧家村1號廢品收購站內收購、儲存大量的醫用點滴袋（鹽水袋）、點滴管（鹽水管）、點滴瓶（鹽水瓶）等醫療廢棄物，伴有難聞氣味，令人作嘔。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1575000/1576020/c03fd53e860e19c335351f_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1575000%2F1576020%2Fc03fd53e860e19c335351f_600.jpg&h=676d5c98&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n警方調查，46歲的張姓嫌犯及從犯於2012年初起從南京數家醫院以每家每月800元至1000元不等的價格回收混有針頭、點滴管的醫療廢棄物，這些販賣廢醫療廢棄物的醫院，甚至不乏公立的三甲醫院。"},{"pid":"f7e9b072fcd8f532130ba80811fc0ae1ded838a5","tid":48457,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T05:44:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1575000/1576020/c03fd53e860e19c335351b_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1575000%2F1576020%2Fc03fd53e860e19c335351b_1024.jpg&h=0b934887&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今年8月30日至31日，專案組民警在收購站及張嫌的車內共清理針頭、點滴管等醫療廢棄物約8.5噸、抗生素類小玻璃瓶約5噸，共約13.5噸。針頭等危險醫療廢物堆積成山，混亂的現場讓人觸目驚心。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1575000/1576020/c03fd53e860e19c3353517_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1575000%2F1576020%2Fc03fd53e860e19c3353517_600.jpg&h=c0b34afb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n塑膠顆粒 銷售到中國各地廠家 <br />\n<br />\n這些醫療廢棄物被製成塑膠顆粒，出售至江蘇宿遷、浙江等地進一步加工。生產出來的塑膠顆粒透過市場和網路，銷售到中國各地的塑膠製品廠家。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1575000/1576020/c03fd53e860e19c3353518_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1575000%2F1576020%2Fc03fd53e860e19c3353518_600.jpg&h=b227d58a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n警方表示，這些塑膠顆粒經過再加工，甚至還被一些黑心廠家用來生產仿冒知名品牌的塑膠玩具、餐具等。警方已在宿遷、浙江發現加工好的免洗餐具。目前，案件正在進一步追蹤調查。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1575000/1576020/c03fd53e860e19c335351a_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1575000%2F1576020%2Fc03fd53e860e19c335351a_600.jpg&h=13f5b517&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41d00bd54087c64a93096b3a576c6c7bbc2bc3ec","tid":48457,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T05:45:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},